<includeonly><h1 style="background:#def;padding:10px">{{{1}}}</h1></includeonly><noinclude>
<code>h1</code> heading with a background color, to make it more distinguishable from <code>h2</code> heading. If implemented via site CSS, this template should be deleted.
==Usage==
<pre>
{{h1|Some Section}}
...
</pre>
----
{{h1|Some Section}}
...
</noinclude>